      • setHeader

        public static void setHeader(org.apache.http.HttpRequest req)
        Set trace id information to HTTP request header.

        If the HTTP request already contains the trace id header, it will not be changed. If the HTTP request does not contain the header, it will be set to the trace id value of the current thread if the current thread has a trace id.

        Parameters:
        req - HTTP request

      • setIdFromRequest

        public static java.lang.String setIdFromRequest(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest r1)
        Set trace id value of the current thread from the HTTP request. If the request does not contain trace id information, a new id will be assigned to the current thread.
        Parameters:
        r1 - HTTP request
        Returns:
        previous trace id value of the current thread. Maybe null.
